    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "The changelog entry for #8658 is:\r\n> Changed timed upgrades to accumulate instead of refreshing if they are granted from different sources. \r\n\r\nWe should have this same behaviour now re multiple sources.  If you want to reset a condition instead of stacking it from the *same* source then you need to explicitly revoke the token that was returned the first time you granted it before you grant it the second time."
