    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Disco power!\r\n\r\n![dancingpowerbarsohyeah](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/1136302/22696427/403654d4-ed4e-11e6-9684-aca8a297a47e.gif)\r\n\r\n```\r\nnapowr:\r\n\tExternalConditions@tesla:\r\n\t\tConditions: tesla\r\n\tStackedCondition@tesla:\r\n\t\tCondition: tesla\r\n\t\tStackedConditions: tesla2, tesla3, tesla4, tesla5\r\n\tPower@default:\r\n\t\tAmount: 150\r\n\t\tRequiresCondition: !tesla\r\n\tPower@charged1:\r\n\t\tAmount: 200\r\n\t\tRequiresCondition: tesla && !tesla2\r\n\tPower@charged2:\r\n\t\tAmount: 250\r\n\t\tRequiresCondition: tesla2 && !tesla3\r\n\tPower@charged3:\r\n\t\tAmount: 300\r\n\t\tRequiresCondition: tesla3 && !tesla4\r\n\tPower@charged4:\r\n\t\tAmount: 350\r\n\t\tRequiresCondition: tesla4 && !tesla5\r\n\tPower@charged5:\r\n\t\tAmount: 375\r\n\t\tRequiresCondition: tesla5\r\n\r\nTrooperCharge:\r\n\tReloadDelay: 25\r\n\tRange: 2c0\r\n#\tReport: iteschaa.wav\tNTM this is annoying as fuck when normalized\r\n\tValidStances: Ally\r\n\tValidTargets: TeslaBoost\r\n\tProjectile: TeslaZap\r\n\t\tBrightSequence: bright-charge\r\n\t\tDimSequence: dim-charge\r\n\t\tDimZaps: 1\r\n\t\tPalette: ra\r\n\tWarhead@charge: GrantExternalCondition\r\n\t\tSpread: 42\r\n\t\tDuration: 55\r\n\t\tCondition: tesla\r\n\t\tValidStances: Ally\r\n\t\tValidTargets: TeslaBoost\r\n```\r\n\r\n#8658's code made so that external conditions would have use their source of origin as a token and not just a single boolean about being external and if the token exists, then refresh the duration. Yet my Tesla Trooper can apply the tesla boost twice and now all my players complain about this disco powerbar."
  },
